LAMMPS (3 Mar 2020)
# Alpha
clear
units		real
dimension 3
boundary        p p p
atom_style	charge
newton on
read_data       O_23.lmp
  triclinic box = (0 0 0) to (15.77 13.6581 25.747) with tilt (7.8845 0 0)
  2 by 2 by 2 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  129 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.00992849 secs

timestep 0.25

